org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation

Class LineAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.NativeObjectContainer
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.AbstractNode
        • org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation.AbstractAnnotation
          • org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation.AbstractXYAnnotation
            • org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation.LineAnnotation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IsDefaultsAnnotation, IsDefaultsLineAnnotation, IsDefaultsXYAnnotation

    public final class LineAnnotation
extends AbstractXYAnnotation
implements IsDefaultsLineAnnotation
    Implements a LINE annotation which draws a line in the a chart.
    Vertical or horizontal lines are supported.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
